data.description: Looking for a home wtih acreage then here you go! 3  bedroom 2 bathrooms on 5 acres. Needs some tender loving attention but has potential. Nice front porch to enjoy your morning coffee and listen to the birds chirp. Large kitchen with area to have a large table and enjoy gatherings. Living room with ifireplace. Laundry room too! Level yard with established trees and plants. Outbuildings convey with property. Property across Toccoa Highway for sale also with 27 acres $148,500.00
